column8: When I digitized this aperture card in 2019, I found an apparently-unfulfilled request for it from 1975, back when the cards were still at the Johnson Space Center prior to being transferred to the National Archives. I couldn't help but wondering about it .... Who wanted this? Why did they want it? Did they ever get it? And if not, why not? Fortunately,youwill never have to do without it!
